    "updated_at": "2016-07-06T21:54:34Z",
    "body": "Can we maybe make it more generic to allow using the same syntax for Windows.  It's generally called \"Start Up\" applications on that side of things so maybe.\n\n`app.setAsStartUpItem([openAsHidden])` \n`app.removeAsStartUpItem()`\n`app.isStartUpItem()`  \n\nBasically just \"login items\" vs \"start up items\"\n"
